This map is in development and will any moment be finished.
I released .VMF below which you can use to edit the map or compile it... you will have to add proper spawnpoints. The map works great with bots!

This map can be either long range or CQB.... If you choose to stay in buildings you will have CQB. If you stay outside you would rather be carrying long range guns. This map will maybe become a Demolition map! This map also requires teamwork if you don't want to become overrun!
